49 template<class Tq>
50 void FluidModel<Tx, Tad>::primvars(const Array3D<const Tq>& Q, Array2D<Tq>& rho, Array2D<Tq>& u, Array2D<Tq>& v, Array2D<Tq>& p, Array2D<Tq>& T, const size_t shifti, const size_t shiftj){
51  auto nic = Q.extent(0);
52  auto njc = Q.extent(1);
53 #pragma omp parallel for
54  for(size_t i=0; i<nic; i++){
55  for(size_t j=0; j<njc; j++){
56  Tq tmp_rho, tmp_u, tmp_v;
57  tmp_rho = Q[i][j][0];
58  tmp_u = Q[i][j][1]/tmp_rho;
59  tmp_v = Q[i][j][2]/tmp_rho;
60  rho[i+shifti][j+shiftj] = tmp_rho;
61  u[i+shifti][j+shiftj] = tmp_u;
62  v[i+shifti][j+shiftj] = tmp_v;
63  p[i+shifti][j+shiftj] = (Q[i][j][3] - 0.5*tmp_rho*(tmp_u*tmp_u + tmp_v*tmp_v))*(gamma-1.0);
64  T[i+shifti][j+shiftj] = get_T_prho(p[i+shifti][j+shiftj], rho[i+shifti][j+shiftj]);
65  }
66  }
67 }
